name: Dear Deer Tree
description:
This Dear Deer tree will add magic to your child's space. It is made of the most INCREDIBLE fabric, that has a low tac adhesive meaning it can be used again and again, and as you see there are so many ways to put your Dear Deer tree together. This tree is made from original hand painted images which means once on the wall looks as if it is painted on. Also all of the items in the images are included in your mural.

You can make one big tall tree, 2 smaller trees, one shorter wide tree...endless REALLY!!

1 x Trunk
10 x branches in varying sizes
1 x Beautiful Purple Deer
1 x Butterfly
1 x Blue sleepy owl
3 x Sets of grass
Approx 30 beautiful leaves in varying sizes

Sheet size is: 65/20" (1700/ 500mm)

name: The Lovely Rose
description:
This is the ultimate girlie wall decor.....floaty, beautiful, romantic and just....LOVELY.

The Lovely Rose comes with everything you see in the picture (except the girls, and is created from our hand painted/collage images.

1 x Lovely Trunk 900mm (35")
1 x Lovely Winged Yellow Cat
2 x Lovely Blue Birds
2 x Lovely Deep Purple Floaty Ribbons
12 x Lovely Red Hearts in varying sizes
35 x Lovely (delicious pale pink to crimson with green leaves) Posies of Roses

Sheet size: A lovely massive 1800/530mm (71/21")

Build 'The Lovely Rose' wall sticker in your unique way or use our pictures for guidance
Like all our decals this is made from fabric and can be changed around and moved many, many times. It is washable, wrinkle and rip proof.

name: Pohutukawa Tree
description:
This beautiful Pohutukawa is New Zealand's native Christmas tree. In the depths of the pacific the sun shines brightly at Christmas time and Pohutukawa flowers glisten bright red on our blue coastlines.
Our version is hand painted and printed onto a very fine fabric vinyl that is removable, reusable and re positionable, it will wrap around corners, it wont crease or rip and best of all wont damage your space.
This tree in all its full flower glory stands at a proud 75"/75" which is a massive 1.9m/1.9m (approx)
The wall graphics will arrive on backing paper 3 branches and approx 80 flowers to create a unique artwork in your space.

name: Babushka Dolls
description:
These gorgeous Babushka dolls originate from our hand painted images. There are small elements to reference different cultures which make them charmingly different.
All our products are made from a glorious fabric decal that will stick to almost any smooth surface and wont rip or wrinkle, and can be moved over and over again! We make them all here in NZ ourselves.

***These dolls come with everything you see in the pic (except the little girl!!) which includes five nesting dolls and 14 lovely flowers

name: Space Odyssey 1968
description:
Ground control to Major Tom....
Planet earth is blue and there is nothing I can do...
'...and I am floating in the most peculiar way...

Well, you get the picture, we are fans of Sci fi and yep David Bowie. Our boys (yeah even the grownup one!) love this retro inspired Space Odyssey. This hand painted action-packed adventure will inspire any imagination....hey I'm a girl and I love it!
Once on the wall looks painted on, this is because all the brush marks are still there. And best of all it can be moved about countless times- an inter-active mural....HOW COOL!!

Sheet size:48/20" 1200/500mm

Mural kit will cover wall approx area:71/60" 1800/1500mm
